        {
            "title": "歐洲股市表現平淡 科技股承壓；達索系統股價下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"661\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xxwT8ho7Wb2cgWA2lK_TOA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6e77d9dad3fca5188ea976ee9d0e782f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市表現平淡，因圍繞<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>對工業軟件顛覆性影響的擔憂抵消了銀行股反彈的影響。達索系統股價下跌10%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克歐洲600指數收盤基本持平。除銀行股外，電信和保險類股表現優於大盤，而媒體和科技股領跌。據彭博匯總數據顯示，因美國和中國市場休市，當日成交量較30日均值低33%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達索系統並非唯一受人工智能焦慮情緒衝擊的企業。西門子股價下跌6.4%，SAP SE下跌2%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"661\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9niLLhiIUw20jfC6nBXjOQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/eac0f6dcd7480a7f1354bfd703a26289\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：跑贏99%同行的基金警示：AI浪潮下 軟件公司倖存者寥寥</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8321be75-9907-3901-9d9f-286347d92cfe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BNP Paribas Wealth Management首席投資策略師Stephan Kemper表示，「人們對人工智能的看法似乎已徹底轉變，從救贖天使變成了致命之吻。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲基準股指持續徘徊於上周創下的紀錄高點下方。財報季表現喜憂參半：企業整體盈利成長態勢良好，但未能達標的公司卻遭受重創。管理層電話會議中提及「人工智能顛覆性影響」的頻率較此前季度幾乎翻倍，印證了這種擔憂已遠超科技領域蔓延開來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Muted as Tech Suffers; Dassault Systemes Falls</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
